{"tid":296820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲仔裸聊又中計　幸未破財","createTime":"2017-06-25T02:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T19:35:57.000Z","uid":42188,"like":499,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54d81efecea9d79ec6f9a3ca2a9b1dbc7b5741de","tid":296820,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:58:26.000Z","msg":"[因涉嫌販運700噸毒品而被政府檢控，繼而棄保潛逃到台灣惟持假證入境遭台警逮捕兼入獄一年與及成為本港頭號通緝犯，亦使自己終身未能返港，及後多次哀求政府撤銷通緝令不果，最終客死異鄉並經常被網民恥笑的馬惜珍，其所創辦的東方日報報道] 90後青年玩裸聊遭勒索，1500港元幸保不失。一名18歲姓黎青年，早前在網上與一名女子聊天時，被對方拍下一些不雅影像，遭對方勒索1500港元，他於昨晚深夜11時許，在牛頭角彩霞邨報案求助。 <br />\n<br />\n警員經初步調查，案件列作勒索，由秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫無人被捕，黎並無金錢損失。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170625/mobile/bkn-20170625060010700-0625_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170625%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170625060010700-0625_00822_001.html&d=9%2BZN6Ff8PaoQpbDbzc4Ei26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=bf6a7ace\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170625/mobile/bkn-20170625060010700-0625_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fc4a373c89cf0069d081da281b20c799d8332e35","tid":296820,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f550ff5f8b79cc34b6841a47fae5342a4239de90","tid":296820,"uid":69535,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"個開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91ec90cd000f4d0a0599073f8e3e69bf394d3e5","tid":296820,"uid":6964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd23649d371399461fec096ccf1330b1a0b40be","tid":296820,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike